dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Sauk_Addresses_2018.gdb'. [Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://data-saukgis.opendata.arcgis.com.
